oji/09.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n未去到呢個lv"},{"pid":"16724c1767b2d1b4df80281cf41f1c860de163e1","tid":220690,"uid":45148,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-28T08:25:33.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>估唔到10年後都沒野超越到00,而加番睇竟然仲高質左<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/09.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n未去到呢個lv</blockquote><br />\n10年內最好係00<br />\n故事 機設 畫面 都中上男神<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f018dc77148e16148ebd838bad4dea34f19d207d","tid":220690,"uid":49163,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-28T08:30:07.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>原來就係要將00推上神枱<br />\n暗黑兵法。岡達獻頭<br />\n<img src=\"https://pbs.twimg.com/media/C8fSOcjVoAEa0sm.jpg:large\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpbs.twimg.com%2Fmedia%2FC8fSOcjVoAEa0sm.jpg%3Alarge&h=06bb580f&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote><br />\n唔係最廢既高達，駕駛員仲要勁個堆<br />\n下場竟然係最慘最屈辱<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"280c38eeefebaa1470813ce8010ad68e3d8d1a81","tid":220690,"uid":49391,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-28T08:31:03.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>er...不太明白</blockquote><br />\n岡媽有病，憎高達到仆街<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-small;\">其實我覺得果個場合冇咩問題</span></blockquote><br />\n好似唔可以入曬岡媽數WO<br />\n我聽過一個版本係佢同監督權鬥緊<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://kknews.cc/zh-hk/entertainment/5mbpnj6.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fkknews.cc%2Fzh-hk%2Fentertainment%2F5mbpnj6.html&d=sV3HumZuViP2rFeoL7TNOC7PofNJLCAwyGXsi6MH%2FEQ%3D&h=55a91ee3\" target=\"_blank\">https://kknews.cc/zh-hk/entertainment/5mbpnj6.html</a>"},{"pid":"cbdf12dc69a7b60785f2e0291ea537c7f90d8019","tid":220690,"uid":49391,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-28T08:32:24.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://kknews.cc/comic/b2zq3an.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fkknews.cc%2Fcomic%2Fb2zq3an.html&d=sV3HumZuViP2rFeoL7TNOC7PofNJLCAwyGXsi6MH%2FEQ%3D&h=0e73e040\" target=\"_blank\">https://kknews.cc/comic/b2zq3an.html</a><br />\n<br />\n那麼罪魁禍首真的只有岡媽一個嗎？事實上根據近期的相關報道，最大的幕後黑手或許並不是她，而是身為動畫監督的長井龍雪。在《高達鐵血》動畫完結之後製作組接受訪談，這期間中岡媽透露了長井龍雪曾經指示出「第二季動畫里鐵華團不要成長」，並突出麥基利斯的「高大形象」，將他作為鐵華團的對手直至結局（雖然麥總最後也領了便當）。"},{"pid":"e9d54a67c472b8637f3d9a0234628d0be2ba7d6e","tid":220690,"uid":38271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-28T08:35:13.000Z","msg":"連SEED都好似高質咗<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/28.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d65ef305ef83273a71d41ab0f5b6006e1f307029","tid":220690,"uid":66076,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-28T08:35:39.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>估唔到10年後都沒野超越到00,而加番睇竟然仲高質左<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/09.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n未去到呢個lv</blockquote><br />\n10年內最好係00<br />\n故事 機設 畫面 都中上男神<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n其實咁情況幾可悲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}